Package org.md2k.mcerebrum.api.core.datakitapi.datasource

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    APPLICATION
    This class defines constants for Application Metadata denoting the type and id.
    APPLICATION.ID
    This embedded class defines the application ids.
    APPLICATION.TYPE
    This embedded class defines the application types, which are sense, analyze and act.
    ApplicationMetaData
    This class defines the ApplicationMetaData object.
    ApplicationMetaData.Builder
    Embedded class that defines the Builder for ApplicationMetaData.
    DataDescriptor
    This class defines the DataDescriptor object.
    DataDescriptor.Builder
    Embedded class that defines the Builder for DataDescriptor.
    DATASOURCE
    This class defines constants for Data Source Metadata denoting the type and id.
    DATASOURCE.ID
    This embedded class defines the data source ids.
    DATASOURCE.METADATA
    This embedded class defines data source metadata constants used by all DataSourceMetaData objects.
    DATASOURCE.TYPE
    This embedded class defines the data source types.
    DataSourceMetaData
    This class defines the DataSourceMetaData object.
    DataSourceMetaData.Builder
    Embedded class that defines the Builder for DataSourceMetaData.
